expression = re.compile(rfc._RFC1123_DATE_REGEX)
bad_dates = ['Jan 21', 'Feb  3', 'Feb 3', 'January 3', 'Feb 3 1997',
    'January 3 1997', 'Something else', '07/23', '07/23/97', '23-Jan-1998',
    '23-07-1998', '23-07-98', '31-Oct-82']
for bad_date in bad_dates:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_date)), msg=
        "Bad date '{d}' didn't match regex".format(d=bad_date))
